com.sarala.mm.job

Class JobStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sarala.mm.job.JobStatus

  • public class JobStatus
extends Object
    Wrapper class to hold the job result and status

    JobStatus provides the option of returning a complex type, depending on the scenario

    • result : holds the final result from job execution
    • userName: user name of the last user who ran a given job
    • jobId: Id of the job whose status is being stored.
    • currentState: @see RunningState
    Author:
    S
